<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Payment Successful! Order Confirmed</title>

  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"/>

  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #2563eb;
      --success: #10b981;
      --success-light: #d1fae5;
      --gray-100: #f8fafc;
      --gray-200: #e2e8f0;
      --gray-700: #334155;
      --gray-900: #0f172a;
      --radius: 16px;
      --shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ecfdf5 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
      color: var(--gray-900);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .success-container {
      max-width: 560px;
      width: 100%;
      background: white;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
      text-align: center;
      animation: floatIn 0.8s ease-out;
    }

    @keyframes floatIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .success-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--success), #34d399);
      padding: 3rem 2rem 2rem;
      color: white;
    }

    .success-header i {
      font-size: 5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: block;
      animation: bounce 2s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes bounce {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
    }

    .success-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .success-header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .success-body {
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      background: white;
    }

    .order-id {
      background: var(--success-light);
      color: #065f46;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      border: 2px dashed #34d399;
    }

    .order-id strong {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--success);
    }

    .details {
      background: var(--gray-100);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--gray-700);
    }

    .details strong {
      color: var(--gray-900);
    }

    .actions {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #1d4ed8;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(37,99,235,0.3);
    }

    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--gray-700);
      border: 2px solid var(--gray-300);
    }

    .btn-outline:hover {
      background: var(--gray-100);
      border-color: var(--gray-400);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      color: var(--gray-500);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .success-header h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
      .success-header i { font-size: 4rem; }
      .actions { flex-direction: column; }
      .btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="success-container">
    <div class="success-header">
      <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
      <h1>Payment Successful!</h1>
      <p>Your order has been confirmed and sent to the supplier instantly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="success-body">
      <div class="order-id">
        Order ID: <strong><%= orderId %></strong>
      </div>

      <div class="details">
        <p><strong>What's next?</strong></p>
        <p>• The supplier has been notified<br>
           • You’ll receive a confirmation email shortly<br>
           • Track your order in real-time from your dashboard</p>
      </div>

      <div class="actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
          <i class="fas fa-shopping-bag"></i> Order More Products
        </a>
        <a href="/my-orders" class="btn btn-outline">
          <i class="fas fa-list"></i> View My Orders
        </a>
      </div>

      <footer>
        Thank you for your purchase! Need help? Contact support anytime.
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Optional: Add subtle confetti effect -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/canvas-confetti@1.9.2/dist/confetti.browser.min.js"></script>
  <script>
    // Trigger confetti on load
    setTimeout(() => {
      confetti({
        particleCount: 100,
        spread: 70,
        origin: { y: 0.6 }
      });
    }, 500);
  </script>
</body>
</html>